&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This is a hybrid position available to individuals residing in the Minneapolis, MN, Eau Claire, WI &amp;amp; Austin, TX metro areas. While the role is primarily hybrid, you may be asked to work occasionally from the Jamf office or a local collaborative workspace alongside other Jamf team members for key events or important in-person engagements. Please note that we are only able to consider applicants who are currently based in the Minneapolis, MN, Eau Claire, WI &amp;amp; Austin, TX metro areas. #LI-Hybrid&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
